name: Baby AlienB
description: Baby AlienB is a crypto asset developed by Bitci Borsa Teknoloji Anonim Limited on Bitcichain. Baby AlienB is a Meme Token project, and its idea of existence is based on a community-centered approach. Baby AlienB aims to grow itself with the power from the community. This digital asset will be driven not by a dedicated core team, but by the demands, governance and decisions of the community in the crypto ecosystem.
